name: Classic Peach and Ivory Handmade Flower Hairpiece
description:
Simplistic and stunning, this handmade organza flower would make a wonderful accessory for your special day. Light peach and ivory in color this piece is accented with ivory ostrich feathers to add just a touch of movement. 

Available in different color choices - if you would like a custom color, please convo me to discuss details.

name: Beautiful Ivory and Cream Vintage Heirloom Brooch Bouquet
description:
Absolutely beautiful ivory and cream colored brooch bouquet. 

A true 'statement' piece for your wedding day! Studded with sparkling vintage brooches this heirloom quality brooch bouquet glistens when the light touches it. A beautiful accent for any bride! 

The handle is wrapped in ivory satin ribbon accented with ivory organza and lace.

Draped from the center is a strand of vintage chain pearls, rhinestones and a pair of tiny vintage swarovski crystal beads.

Brooch bouquets are special for so many reasons...they make meaningful keepsakes after your wedding, they add just the right amount of sparkle to your special day and thereafter as well! They make beautiful display pieces and can be handed down through generations...you can also add your own sentimental pieces to carry down the isle with you. Brooch Bouquets can usually sum up your something old, new, borrowed and blue in one accessory!

name: One of a Kind Bohemian, Vintage Style Handmade Flower Headpiece
description:
One of a kind vintage inspired bohemian flower headpiece. Adorned with champagne, ivory and cream handmade flowers on either side of a drop chain of silver and pearls. This piece would be perfect for a beach, vintage or bohemian style wedding, or would work for everyday wear as well!
Hand beaded swarovski crystals and pearls are throughout to add a touch of sparkle and elegance.

name: Chantilly Lace Cap / Headband
description: Beautiful Handmade Chantilly Lace Headpiece with Chantilly Lace, Handmade Chiffon Flowers, Feathers, Crystals and more.

name: Hand Beaded Peach and Ivory Flower Headband with Drop Pearls and Rhinestone Accents
description:
This headband would be a beautiful addition to your wedding day ensemble! Hand Beaded swarovski crystals and pearls along with fresh water pearls adorn the headband while hand made flowers cascade along the side. 

Vintage millinery flowers, rhinestone chain and pearls are incorporated to accent and allow movement and sparkle in the piece as well. A one of a kind accessory!
